    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels wonderful on the road. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
