      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring the mechanical vitals are robust and ready for high-RPM operation. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and predictable lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering the visceral analog experience this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
