    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This premium sport sedan is the perfect blend of performance and everyday reliability. Finished in a timeless metallic coat, the exterior maintains a deep shine, showing only the minor, superficial character marks one would expect from a well-loved vehicle. The interior is exceptionally clean; the leather seats remain supple and supportive, and the cabin is free of any odors or significant wear. All electronic components, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a composed, comfortable ride. This car has been garage-kept and non-smoker owned, ensuring the interior trim and dashboard remain in excellent shape. It is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
